                     <interp inst="t17560603-14-off74" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp>
               stealing one silver watch, value 40 s. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17560603-14-victim135" type="victimName">
                           James 
                           Wheeler 
                        <interp inst="t17560603-14-victim135" type="surname" value="Wheeler"></interp>
